In large microwave safe bowl, melt margarine, one cup of chocolate chips, and marshmallows on HIGH for about 2 minutes, stirring after 1 minute. Stir vanilla into mixture until smooth. Add KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal, stirring until well coated. Shape half cup of mixture into ball, inserting a wooden stick. Refrigerate until firm. Melt remaining cup of chocolate and shortening in a small sauce pan over low heat. Dip the bottom of each ball into chocolate and decorate with candy sprinkles. Refrigerate until firm.